<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .booking-id {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Exhibitor Booking Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{contactPerson}},</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for submitting your exhibitor booking request for <strong>{{eventName}}</strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="booking-id">
                <p><strong>Booking Reference:</strong> {{bookingId}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Your booking request for <strong>{{companyName}}</strong> has been received and is currently under review. Our team will contact you shortly to discuss the details and next steps.</p>
            
            <h3>What's Next?</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Our team will review your application</li>
                <li>You'll receive a confirmation email with space allocation details</li>
                <li>Payment instructions will be provided</li>
                <li>Setup and exhibition guidelines will be shared</li>
            </ol>
            
            <p>If you have any immediate questions, please don't hesitate to contact our exhibitor support team.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 